D. \left \{ \left \{ 1 \right \} ,\left \{ 2 \right \},\left \{ a \right \},\left \{ 1,2 \right \},\left \{ 1,a \right \},\left \{ 2,a \right \},\left \{ 1,2,a \right \}\right \}

